OL,3,CPope paves way for London-born Carlo
OL,4,CAcutis to be the first millennial saint
OL,6,FThe Pope has paved the way for a
OL,7,FLondon born teenager, who died from
OL,8,Fleukemia, to become the first
OL,9,Fmillennial saint.
OL,11,FCarlo Acutis died when he was 15 years
OL,12,Fold, and living in Italy, after
OL,13,Fspending much of his short life
OL,14,Fsharing the message of Christ on a
OL,15,Fwebsite he created from scratch.
