OL,3,CPope paves way for London-born Carlo
OL,4,CAcutis to be the first millennial saint
OL,6,FBut after his death, in 2006, Acutis
OL,7,Fwould go on to perform his own two
OL,8,Fmiracles, meaning he has passed the
OL,9,Fthreshold to become a saint.
OL,11,FAfter touching one of Acutis's T-
OL,12,Fshirts a seven-year-old boy from
OL,13,FBrazil made a miraculous recovery from
OL,14,Fa rare pancreatic disorder. A priest
OL,15,Fhad also prayed to Acutis for the
OL,16,Fpoorly boy, the Guardian reports.
OL,18,FThe Pope later verified Acutis was the
OL,19,Fsource of this miracle and he was put
OL,20,Fon the path to sainthood.
