OL,6,FCarlo Acutis' beatification ceremony
OL,7,Fin 2020
OL,9,FIn 2020 he was beatified - which is
OL,10,Fthe official recognition that he lived
OL,11,Fa holy life in the Catholic Church and
OL,12,Fis usually the step before becoming a
OL,13,Fsaint.
OL,15,FA procession walked through the
OL,16,Fstreets of Assisi, Italy, and he was
OL,17,Fblessed and laid to rest in an open
OL,18,Fcasket.
