OL,3,CPope paves way for London-born Carlo
OL,4,CAcutis to be the first millennial saint
OL,6,FOn July 8, 2022, a woman called
OL,7,FLiliana, from Costa Rica, prayed at
OL,8,FCarlo's tomb in Assisi, as her
OL,9,Fdaughter Valeria, was fighting for her
OL,10,Flife after falling off her bicycle in
OL,11,FFlorence, where she was attending
OL,12,Funiversity.
OL,14,FShe had suffered severe head trauma -
OL,15,Fshe needed had craniotomy surgery and
OL,16,Fthe removal of the right occipital
OL,17,Fbone to reduce pressure on her brain.
OL,19,FDoctors said she had a very low chance
OL,20,Fof survival.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/8
