OL,3,CPope paves way for London-born Carlo
OL,4,CAcutis to be the first millennial saint
OL,6,FOn the same day her mother prayed to
OL,7,FCarlo, the hospital informed her that
OL,8,FValeria had started breathing again,
OL,9,Fthe next day, she began to move and
OL,10,Fpartially regain her speech.
OL,12,FOn July 18, a CAT scan proved her
OL,13,Fhemorrhage had disappeared, and on
OL,14,FAugust 11, Valeria was moved to
OL,15,Frehabilitation therapy.
OL,17,FThis has now been verified as Acutis'
OL,18,Fsecond miracle.
