OL,3,CPope paves way for London-born Carlo
OL,4,CAcutis to be the first millennial saint
OL,6,FOn Thursday, Cardinal Marcello
OL,7,FSemeraro, who is in charge of who
OL,8,Fbecomes a saint, met with Pope Francis
OL,9,Fwho approved Acutis' assentation.
OL,11,FDuring his short life Acutis always
OL,12,Fput others before himself - he used
OL,13,Fhis first savings to buy a sleeping
OL,14,Fbag for a homeless man he often saw on
OL,15,Fthe way to Mass and would often help
OL,16,Fpeople who were struggling.
OL,18,FHe also loved playing football, video
OL,19,Fgames, and his family say he couldn't
OL,20,Fsay "no" to Nutella or to ice cream.
